articles.title: Myanmar’s military junta charge hundreds with breaking election law as voting date nears - CNN
articles.description: Myanmar’s military government has charged more than 200 people with violating the Southeast Asian country’s voting law ahead of a general election at the end of the month, keeping up pressure on opponents of the polls.
